dct_title_s: Davao & Santa Ana, Philippine Islands, chartered city of Davao, Mindanao Island. A.M.S. S901
dct_description_sm: AMS 2. Alternate title: Davao & Santa Ana. In upper left margin: Philippine city plans 1:6,000. Polyconic projection. Compiled from Town of Davao, OSS, 1943, USC&GS Topographic Field Survey Sheets, 1:5,000, P1842 A & B, 1930; oblique photography, 1935-36; vertical mosaic, prior to 1940.
dct_publisher_sm: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1944.
